Yes. We can send a carriage there.

734
00:32:46,420 --> 00:32:47,460
Like what Xuan did.

735
00:32:47,460 --> 00:32:49,260
He doesn't go up the mountain with his own legs,
but with horses.

736
00:32:49,460 --> 00:32:50,460
I should've learned it sooner.

737
00:32:50,460 --> 00:32:51,460
Too bad.

738
00:32:51,620 --> 00:32:54,180
I'll get them to pack everything up.

739
00:32:54,180 --> 00:32:55,460
Sure. Pack all of them.

740
00:33:01,580 --> 00:33:02,300
Sufang.

741
00:33:02,660 --> 00:33:03,980
I have something to ask you.

742
00:33:03,980 --> 00:33:04,660
What nice food and fun stuff

743
00:33:04,660 --> 00:33:05,860
can I get in the palace?

744
00:33:05,860 --> 00:33:06,660
When my mother is here tomorrow,

745
00:33:06,660 --> 00:33:07,860
I want to show her around.

746
00:33:07,980 --> 00:33:09,420
Nice food?

747
00:33:09,900 --> 00:33:12,260
Imperial Chef Chai
is one of the best cooks in the world.

748
00:33:12,260 --> 00:33:14,620
Maybe he can cook for your mother.

749
00:33:14,620 --> 00:33:16,580
His cooking lacks flavor.

750
00:33:16,580 --> 00:33:17,820
I'm sure my mother won't like it.

751
00:33:18,300 --> 00:33:19,860
Then, maybe Your Majesty can bring Madam
to Yufang Garden.

752
00:33:19,860 --> 00:33:21,380
The flowers have just blossomed,

753
00:33:21,380 --> 00:33:23,260
and they make the place really beautiful.

754
00:33:23,580 --> 00:33:24,940
What's so nice about Yufang Garden?

755
00:33:24,940 --> 00:33:25,740
It's too small.

756
00:33:26,220 --> 00:33:27,980
I should bring you to Xianpa Village one day.

757
00:33:27,980 --> 00:33:29,660
It's the harvest season for rapeseed.

758
00:33:29,660 --> 00:33:30,660
The view is spectacular.

759
00:33:31,220 --> 00:33:33,460
What about the Astronomical Observatory?

760
00:33:33,460 --> 00:33:34,980
You can overlook the entire palace from there,

761
00:33:34,980 --> 00:33:36,100
and at the same time,
enjoy the view of the back mountain.

762
00:33:36,100 --> 00:33:37,780
It takes more than 200 steps to reach the top.

763
00:33:37,980 --> 00:33:39,660
Are you trying to tire my mother out?

764
00:33:40,180 --> 00:33:41,260
Sorry, Your Majesty.

765
00:33:41,260 --> 00:33:42,900
That is all I could think of.

766
00:33:43,220 --> 00:33:43,860
Forget it.

767
00:33:43,980 --> 00:33:45,420
I'll ask Xuan later.

768
00:33:45,940 --> 00:33:47,380
Why is Xuan not back yet?

769
00:33:47,380 --> 00:33:48,580
The court assembly should've ended by now.

770
00:33:48,580 --> 00:33:50,180
I think His Majesty will be here soon.

771
00:33:50,780 --> 00:33:51,460
Your Majesty,

772
