to Xuan's guidance,

777
00:34:00,980 --> 00:34:02,820
I have already memorized the palace rules

778
00:34:02,820 --> 00:34:04,820
and mastered the etiquette.

779
00:34:04,980 --> 00:34:06,980
All I have to do now is to get as much rest

780
00:34:06,980 --> 00:34:07,580
as I can.

781
00:34:07,580 --> 00:34:08,660
Really?

782
00:34:09,420 --> 00:34:10,900
Then, I can rest assured.

783
00:34:11,100 --> 00:34:13,420
Look at how confident you are, Your Majesty,

784
