I'm sure you've memorized
the names of all the imperial family members.

785
00:34:16,940 --> 00:34:17,620
Imperial family?

786
00:34:19,260 --> 00:34:20,460
It's just a few names.

787
00:34:20,460 --> 00:34:21,660
I can memorize them tomorrow morning.

788
00:34:21,660 --> 00:34:22,580
It's going to be fine.

789
00:34:23,020 --> 00:34:23,820
Your Majesty.

790
00:34:23,980 --> 00:34:25,540
I think it will be too late by then.

791
00:34:26,020 --> 00:34:27,620
How many family members does he have?

792
00:34:27,940 --> 00:34:30,460
There are tens of them.

793
00:34:34,540 --> 00:34:36,700
Long live Your Majesty.

794
